msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.55:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga"
msgstr "6. Comprehension"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 55. Paṭhamamahāpathavīsutta → paṭhavisuttaṃ (bj) | paṭhavī 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.55:0.3"
msgid "55. Paṭhamamahāpathavīsutta"
msgstr "55. The Earth (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.462"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: mahāpathaviyā → mahāpaṭhaviyā (bj)
msgctxt "sn56.55:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso mahāpathaviyā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā "
"upanikkhipeyya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose a person was to place seven clay balls the size of "
"jujube seeds on the great earth."

msgctxt "sn56.55:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.55:1.3"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yā vā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā upanikkhittā, "
"ayaṃ vā mahāpathavī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds, or the great "
"earth?”"

msgctxt "sn56.55:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ—mahāpathavī; appamattikā satta "
"kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā upanikkhittā."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the great earth is certainly more. The seven clay balls the size of "
"jujube seeds are tiny."

msgctxt "sn56.55:1.5"
msgid ""
"Saṅkhampi na upenti, upanidhampi na upenti, kalabhāgampi na upenti "
"mahāpathaviṃ upanidhāya satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā upanikkhittā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the great earth, they can’t be reckoned or compared, they’re not "
"even a fraction.”"

msgctxt "sn56.55:1.6"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa … pe …"
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple …"

msgctxt "sn56.55:1.7"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.55:1.8"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
